response:
Feedback Summary (2 comments):

General Comments:
1. // OpenSSL includes (will be available after vcpkg installs OpenSSL)
#include <openssl/evp.h>
#include <openssl/rand.h>
#include <openssl/bio.h>
#include <openssl/buffer.h>
#include <openssl/x509.h>  // For i2d_PUBKEY() and d2i_PUBKEY()

These includes in "C:\p4\Personal\SD\Engine\Code\Engine\Network\KADIAuthenticationUtility.cpp" was causing a problem because it's from "C:\vcpkg" on my local machine. This won't work because other people's computer might not have vcpkg installed. I want to fix this, so please add fixing this in the design.md.
2. No full hidden surface removal. [ Hidden surface removal ]

This was a requirement in spec A5, but I think we didn't implement it correctly. Please make sure we implement this.

